    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. This car is in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs like a charm, and is perfect if you\u2019re looking for something reliable and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so come by, say hi, and take it for a test drive\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
