    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i is a well-maintained example that balances luxury with reliable performance. Finished in a sophisticated Deep Sea Blue Metallic, the exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. The interior features Canberra Beige Dakota Leather that has been regularly conditioned; there is slight creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, but the cabin is otherwise pristine and remains free of any smoke or pet odors. All interior electronics, including the wide-screen navigation, heated seats, and the expansive panoramic sunroof, are fully operational. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health with a documented service history. It recently received a fresh oil change and new brake pads. The turbocharged inline-six engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. Included are two keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a set of all-weather floor mats. This vehicle offers a premium driving experience for a buyer who values a documented maintenance pedigree.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
