    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape, ready to take you on your next big adventure! It runs like a dream and has been super well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a solid, dependable ride that looks great and feels even better to drive, you've found it! I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how much life this beauty has left. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 29500.0,
